      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are privileged to present this peerless example, maintained to an exacting standard that transcends the typical pre-owned category. This vehicle represents the definitive intersection of performance and preservation, featuring an immaculate exterior finish and a cabin that retains its original showroom integrity. Every mechanical component has been subjected to a rigorous validation process, ensuring it meets the requirements of the most discerning collector. For those who demand an uncompromising automotive experience, this specimen stands as a testament to diligent stewardship and remains in superlative condition.",
