    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54B32 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a fully serviced dual-VANOS system. This specimen features a reinforced rear subframe and a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox delivering power to a variable M-differential. The chassis retains its factory-spec torsional rigidity with zero oxidative stress on the undercarriage. Every bushing, seal, and fluid line is in peak operational state, ensuring the precise turn-in and throttle response this platform is celebrated for. A concours-level example with flawless paint depth and an immaculate interior.",
